policy_name_s: Privileged Machines Exposed to the Internet
recommendation_s:
Validate that the resource exposed must remain so to fulfil its function.
Validate the information this resource contains to prevent sensitive leaks of data.
If the resource should not be accessible, block any of the networks rules from accepting public internet.
 Remember that a higher level resource might block other related resources from accessing the internet as well.
  It is possible to block a resource from the public internet by attaching a security group.
description_s:
EC2 Instance frontend_views in AWS is exposed to the internet. The instance has the following role assigned: ec2_s3_full_access
Full Exposure Path:
| Resource | Type | | -------- |-------- | | prod_na-igw | Gateway | | customer-application-lb | LoadBalancer | | frontend_views | VirtualMachine |
